# DESIGN PHILOSOPHY

## The 100ms Rule
Every interaction responds visually in under 100ms.
Never show a loading spinner in the primary flow.
Optimistic UI everywhere.

## Animation Rules
- CSS transforms only - never layout properties
- Spring physics not linear easing
- Stagger card entrances 50ms apart
- Numbers use countUp animation always
- The "agent found them" event gets a 500ms 
  golden flash before the card appears

## The Opening Sequence Is The Product
The first 10 seconds will be shared on X.
Treat them accordingly.
